AUDIO: 'it\'s not perfect. People like it because it feels simple. It\'s privacy first. That\'s huge. And if you self-host it, you get full control over everything. Then, it still comes with tradeoffs,'

[04:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'just like any open-source tool. There\'s a learning curve if you go deeper, especially on the self-hosting side of things. There\'s no built-in request inspection like ngrok. And depending on your setup, you might notice a bit of latency. But, even with those downsides,'

[05:00] [scene:talk]
